prompt_text: Describe the scene of an airport.
content_text: Everything was chaos and the airport, The planes were running late because it was raining really hard. People were waiting with their backs, lots of tourists with their passports, trying to board their planes. They were all desperate and thought that they were going to be late to their destinations. People were waiting, playing games, listening to music. Talking to other people. Buying food and just trying to eat distract themselves of their situation. After a couple hours, the planes.
